{"title": "File Upload & Download", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "ftp-protocol/get-and-put-files", "html": "<h1 id=\"file-upload-download\">🆕 File Upload &amp; Download</h1>\n<h2 id=\"list-files-in-a-directory\">List Files in a Directory</h2>\n<p>List files in a specific directory using FTP.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--ls<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>DIRECTORY<span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--ls\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.3<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Directory<span class=\"w\"> </span>Listing\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span>drwx------<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1001</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">1001</span><span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">4096</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Sep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">15</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"m\">2021</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Maildir\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span>-rw-rw-r--<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1001</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">1001</span><span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">4006</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Sep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">15</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"m\">2021</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>README.txt\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span>-rw-rw-r--<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1001</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">1001</span><span class=\"w\">           </span><span class=\"m\">39</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Sep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">15</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"m\">2021</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp_flag.thm\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"download-a-file\">Download a File</h2>\n<p>Download a file from the FTP server.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--get<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>FILE<span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--get<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp_flag.thm\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.3<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Downloaded:<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp_flag.thm\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"upload-a-file\">Upload a File</h2>\n<p>Upload a file to the FTP server providing you have relevant permissions</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--put<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>LOCAL_FILE<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>REMOTE_FILE<span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--put<span class=\"w\"> </span>test.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>test.txt\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.3<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>-<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Failed<span class=\"w\"> </span>to<span class=\"w\"> </span>upload<span class=\"w\"> </span>file.<span class=\"w\"> </span>Response:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"m\">550</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Permission<span class=\"w\"> </span>denied.<span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "🆕 File Upload &amp; Download List Files in a Directory List files in a specific directory using FTP. nxc ftp &lt;target&gt; -u &lt;username&gt; -p &#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39; --ls [ DIRECTORY ] Example: nxc ftp &lt;target&gt; -u &lt;username&gt; -p…", "tags": []}